KitKat::

She had heard the transmission and decided to head for his location.  
She walked over to the two male bots and looked at them. hand on hip 
and tail swishing,"Hello gentlebots."  She looked at Carnatron and 
then to Perceptor. "What's going on?"

Perceptor:

Perceptor arrived to Carmatron's location.

"Carnatron, I suppose" said the male
